Gibson's Gourmet Burgers and Ribs is number one in the Guinness Book of Records for their astonishing 207 varieties of milkshakes. CAPE TOWN - A few months ago, a Cape Town burger restaurant attempted one of the sweetest records -- that of the most varieties of milkshakes commercially available. And the attempt has paid off, earning it the top spot in the Guinness Book of Records. Gibson's Gourmet Burgers and Ribs is number one for their astonishing 207 varieties of milkshakes.
Their flavours range from Berries to Chocolate and even Custard and Jelly to name a few.
OwnersÂ Ian Halfon and Doron Duveen pride themselves on catering for everyone.